- **Decentralized Reputation System** : Users can build and manage their reputation across multiple dApps.
- **Trustless Interactions**: Facilitates trustless interactions between parties using smart contracts.
- **Reputation Tokens**: Users earn reputation tokens (RPT) based on their interactions and contributions.
- **Staking Mechanism**: Users can stake tokens to increase their trust score.
- **Governance**: Community-driven governance model for protocol upgrades and changes.
